Some kind of screaming,
like a child's voice.

824
01:10:49,249 --> 01:10:50,716
你怎么做？
What did you do?

825
01:10:51,251 --> 01:10:52,582
我下楼
l went...

826
01:10:52,786 --> 01:10:55,482
走出屋外
...downstairs. Outside.

827
01:10:57,624 --> 01:11:00,218
我偷进了壳仓
l crept up into the barn.

828
01:11:00,427 --> 01:11:03,624
我很害怕看进去，但又必须看
l was so scared to look inside,
but l had to.

829
01:11:04,764 --> 01:11:08,063
你看见什么？克丽丝？
And what did you see, Clarice?
What did you see?

830
01:11:09,502 --> 01:11:10,799
一些羔羊
Lambs.

831
01:11:12,005 --> 01:11:13,666
它们在尖叫
They were screaming.

832
01:11:14,241 --> 01:11:17,005
他们在宰杀那些羔羊？
They were slaughtering
the spring lambs?

833
01:11:17,544 --> 01:11:19,273
而它们在尖叫
And they were screaming.

834
01:11:20,614 --> 01:11:22,309
那你就跑掉了？
And you ran away?

835
01:11:22,515 --> 01:11:26,349
不是，最初我想释放它们
No. First l tried to free them.

836
01:11:27,020 --> 01:11:29,454
我打开它们的闸门
l opened the gate to their pen.

837
01:11:29,656 --> 01:11:33,092
