They wouldn't run.

838
01:11:33,293 --> 01:11:35,784
但你可以走，你也走了
是不是？
But you could and you did, didn't you?

839
01:11:36,596 --> 01:11:39,997
是的，我抱起一只羊就拔足逃跑
Yes. l took one lamb
and l ran away as fast as l could.

840
01:11:40,200 --> 01:11:41,997
你去哪里？
Where were you going, Clarice?

841
01:11:42,202 --> 01:11:45,194
