...and it was very cold.
lt was very cold.

843
01:11:50,243 --> 01:11:51,369
我以为...
l thought....

844
01:11:52,279 --> 01:11:54,839
我以为，至少可救到一只羊
l thought if l could save just one...

845
01:11:56,850 --> 01:11:58,442
但它很重
...but he was so heavy.

846
01:11:59,552 --> 01:12:01,042
真的很重
He was so heavy.

847
01:12:06,359 --> 01:12:10,295
我走不了几哩路
警长的车就把我截住
l didn't get more than a few miles
when the sheriffs car picked me up.

848
01:12:13,466 --> 01:12:17,664
