Lecter's gone, sarge.

923
01:20:40,271 --> 01:20:42,068
囚犯失踪了
Prisoner is missing.

924
01:20:42,273 --> 01:20:43,740
鲍尔的配枪不见了
Boyle's gun is gone.

925
01:20:44,075 --> 01:20:46,543
重复，莱达持械失踪了
Repeat. Lecter is missing and armed.

926
01:20:46,744 --> 01:20:48,541
