He stripped the bed.

927
01:20:48,980 --> 01:20:51,744
可能用来做绳，搜查所有窗户
Might be making a rope.
Check all the windows.

928
01:20:51,950 --> 01:20:54,248
救护车，在哪里？
Where the fuck is my ambulance?

929
01:20:54,719 --> 01:20:56,209
他仍活着的
He's alive.

930
01:20:56,821 --> 01:20:59,085
戴德警官，他仍活着！
Sergeant Tate! He's alive!

931
01:20:59,457 --> 01:21:02,654
