Now talk to him, damn it!

934
01:21:08,233 --> 01:21:10,497
莱达持械失踪了
Lecter is missing and armed.

935
01:21:10,702 --> 01:21:14,536
-庞毕...你听到我吗？
-他拿了鲍尔的配枪
-Pembry. Pembry, can you hear me?
-He took Boyle's gun.

936
01:21:14,739 --> 01:21:17,765
