Catherine Martin?

1174
01:45:21,476 --> 01:45:22,841
是！
Yes!

1175
01:45:24,545 --> 01:45:25,807
联邦调查局
FBl.

1176
01:45:26,013 --> 01:45:27,310
你安全了
You're safe.

1177
01:45:27,515 --> 01:45:30,484
安全个屁！快救我出去
Safe, shit! Get me out of here!

1178
01:45:45,600 --> 01:45:47,465
你没事的，他在哪里？
You're all right. Where is he?

1179
01:45:47,668 --> 01:45:50,637
我怎么知道？快救我出去！
How the fuck should l know?
Just get me out of here!

1180
01:45:50,838 --> 01:45:54,001
凯瑟琳，你静一点，叫那只狗别吵
Catherine, you've gotta be quiet!
Now, shut that dog up!

1181
01:45:54,208 --> 01:45:56,267
快救我出去！
Just get me out of here!

1182
01:45:57,378 --> 01:45:58,538
我的天
Oh, my God.

1183
01:46:00,982 --> 01:46:05,009
凯瑟琳，我会救你的，但你听着
Catherine, l'm gonna get you out.
But right now, you listen to me.

1184
01:46:05,219 --> 01:46:09,221
我要离开一会，很快回来
l've gotta leave. l'll be right back.

1185
01:46:09,221 --> 01:46:11,621
不，不要丢下我
你这个婊子，别走！
No! Don't you leave me here,
you fucking bitch! No!

1186
01:46:11,657 --> 01:46:13,181
不要丢下我！
Don't you leave me here!

1187
01:46:13,392 --> 01:46:16,122
这个家伙是疯的！
This guy is fucking crazy!

1188
01:46:18,497 --> 01:46:23,332
等一下，我要离开这里
Wait! l gotta get out of here!

1189
01:46:24,837 --> 01:46:25,826
求求你！
Please!

1190
01:46:26,038 --> 01:46:30,737
凯瑟琳！其他的探员会很快到达的
Catherine! The other officers
will be here any minute now.

1191
01:46:30,943 --> 01:46:34,674
不要走！求求你
Wait! Don't go! Please!

1192
01:46:34,880 --> 01:46:36,177
别吵！
Quiet!

1193
01:46:38,484 --> 01:46:41,044
天啊...
Oh, God! Oh, God!

1194
01:50:04,990 --> 01:50:06,548
（恐怖）

1195
01:50:06,759 --> 01:50:09,057
（比尔剥下第五个人的皮）

1196
01:50:36,855 --> 01:50:39,323
-你没事吧？
-小事，不要紧，我没事
-You okay?
-Gunpowder. lt's nothing, l'm okay.

1197
01:50:39,525 --> 01:50:42,551
史达琳探员，你怎么追查到
水牛比尔在这里的？
Agent Starling, how did you
track Buffalo Bill here?

1198
01:50:42,761 --> 01:50:46,458
（司法部联邦调查局）

1199
01:50:48,867 --> 01:50:51,734
克丽丝史达琳
Clarice M. Starling.

1200
01:50:53,906 --> 01:50:55,203
恭喜你
Congratulations.

1201
01:51:08,720 --> 01:51:11,484
昂利史蒂文
Ernest W. Stevens.

1202
01:51:29,406 --> 01:51:31,306
特种探员克丽丝史达琳！
Special Agent Starling!

1203
01:51:31,709 --> 01:51:33,609
-特种探员麦普
-有电话找你
-Special Agent Mapp.
-Phone call.

1204
01:51:33,811 --> 01:51:35,142
谢谢，失陪
Thank you. Excuse me.

1205
01:51:35,346 --> 01:51:36,608
史达琳
Starling.

1206
01:51:39,450 --> 01:51:42,317
替我们拍照好吗？
Pilch, could you take our picture?

1207
01:51:42,553 --> 01:51:43,611
好的
Sure.

1208
01:51:45,556 --> 01:51:47,683
我只想说声恭喜
l just wanted to say congratulations.

1209
01:51:48,058 --> 01:51:51,619
我不擅应酬，所以我要走了
l'm no good at this kind of thing,
so l'm gonna duck out of here.

1210
01:51:52,096 --> 01:51:53,723
好的
Okay. Sure.

1211
01:51:55,232 --> 01:51:56,893
谢谢，葛先生
Thank you, Mr. Crawford.

1212
01:52:04,708 --> 01:52:06,938
令尊今天定会很骄傲
Your father would've been proud today.

1213
01:52:10,247 --> 01:52:11,976
别忘了接听电话
Don't forget your phone call.

1214
01:52:16,620 --> 01:52:17,985
史达琳
Starling.

1215
01:52:18,222 --> 01:52:19,814
克丽丝...
Well, Clarice...

1216
01:52:20,357 --> 01:52:22,848
那些羔羊停止尖叫了吗？
...have the lambs stopped screaming?

1217
01:52:23,294 --> 01:52:24,420
莱达医生？
Dr. Lecter?

1218
01:52:24,628 --> 01:52:27,654
不必追踪这个电话
我不会讲太久
Don't bother with a trace.
l won't be on long enough.

1219
01:52:31,168 --> 01:52:33,295
莱达医生，你在哪里？
Where are you, Dr. Lecter?

1220
01:52:33,504 --> 01:52:35,369
我不打算找你了
l have no plans to call on you.

1221
01:52:35,573 --> 01:52:38,041
有了你，这个世界更加有趣
The world's more interesting
with you in it.

1222
01:52:38,576 --> 01:52:41,568
你保重，日后报答我吧
So you take care now
to extend me the same courtesy.

1223
01:52:41,779 --> 01:52:44,304
我不能作那个承诺的
You know l can't make that promise.

1224
01:52:44,782 --> 01:52:47,148
但愿我们可以多聊一会
l do wish we could chat longer...

1225
01:52:48,452 --> 01:52:51,148
但我找了个老朋友吃晚饭
...but l'm having
an old friend for dinner.

1226
01:52:52,623 --> 01:52:53,885
再见
Bye.

1227
01:52:54,358 --> 01:52:55,689
莱达医生！
Dr. Lecter!

1228
01:52:58,195 --> 01:52:59,628
莱达医生
Dr. Lecter.

1229
01:53:01,832 --> 01:53:03,299
莱达医生
Dr. Lecter.

1230
01:53:05,236 --> 01:53:06,794
莱达医生？
Dr. Lecter?

1231
01:53:07,838 --> 01:53:09,237
抱歉，对不起
Excuse me. l'm sorry.

1232
01:53:09,440 --> 01:53:11,101
保安系统安排了吗？
The security system's set up?

1233
01:53:11,308 --> 01:53:13,970
-我们有严密保安的
-谢谢
-We have the big shot security.
-l appreciate it.

1234
01:58:12,876 --> 01:58:19,679
（谨把本片献给崔威尔逊）

